    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s been well-loved and is still looking sharp and running super smoothly. Whether you're zipping through your daily commute or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to hit the road with you! It\u2019s got plenty of life left and is just waiting for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
