    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss and reflects a history of regular washing and waxing, showing only the minor stone chips and light surface marks typical of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the bolsters on the seats remain firm, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats throughout its life. All electronic features\u2014including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and power accessories\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, characterized by a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has seen oil changes at every recommended interval. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a complete, honest car that has been cared for by a meticulous owner and is ready for many more miles of dependable service.",
